<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #3498db; /* Changed background color to blue */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .total {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 style="color: #fff;">Order Confirmation</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333;">Your ELearning order is confirmed.</p>
        <p style="color: #333;">Thank you for your order. We are pleased to confirm that your order has been received and is currently being processed.</p>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Order #</th>
                <th>Order Date</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><%= order._id %></td>
                <td><%= order.date %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Course Detail</th>
                <th>Qty</th>
                <th>Cost</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><%=order.name %></td>
                <td>1</td>
                <td>$ <%= order.price %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <p class="footer" style="color: #fff;">Thank you for choosing us. If you have any questions, please contact our customer support.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
